{"id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0003", "text": "夜更深 不敢送贈的吻", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 3, 3, 9, 4, 2, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["je6", "sam1", "bat1", "gam2", "sung3", "zang6", "dik1", "man5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "夜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更深", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不敢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "送贈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吻", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "明目張膽", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_262", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0004", "text": "全憑我手中的偷拍照 營造着你那體溫", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 5, 9, 3, 3, 3, 4, 4, 0, 2, 2, 5, 5, 9, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cyun4", "pang4", "ngo5", "sau2", "zung1", "dik1", "tau1", "paak3", "ziu3", "jing4", "zou6", "zoek6", "nei5", "naa5", "tai2", "wan1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "全憑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "手中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "偷拍照", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "營造", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "體溫", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "明目張膽", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_262", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0005", "text": "我 如果想一世人 和你過", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 0, 9, 9, 3, 4, 0, 0, 5, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "jyu4", "gwo2", "soeng2", "jat1", "sai3", "jan4", "wo4", "nei5", "gwo3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如果", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "世人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "和", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "明目張膽", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_262", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0006", "text": "平時就要企後幾吋 去幻想 別要摸", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 5, 2, 9, 4, 4, 2, 9, 2, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ping4", "si4", "zau6", "jiu3", "kei5", "hau6", "gei2", "cyun3", "heoi3", "waan6", "soeng2", "bit6", "jiu3", "mo2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "平時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "企後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吋", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幻想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "摸", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "明目張膽", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_262", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0007", "text": "若有 一天公開 明目張膽的愛", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 3, 0, 2, 3, 9, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["joek6", "jau5", "jat1", "tin1", "gung1", "hoi1", "ming4", "muk6", "zoeng1", "daam2", "dik1", "oi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "若有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "公開", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "明目張膽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "明目張膽", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_262", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0008", "text": "我怕會讓你 太意外", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 2, 5, 4, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "paa3", "joeng6", "nei5", "taai3", "ji3", "ngoi6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "意外", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "明目張膽", "artists": ["Ho"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_262", "prev_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_SG8_MjYy_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
